for tips 
Add media files in the same folder (e.g., tip-2025-11.jpg or tip-2025-11.mp4 with a poster JPG).

In the Featured section at the top, replace the image/video + quote + month label.

Move last month’s content into a new <details class="tip-card">…</details> block in the Previous Months section.

Keep the newest previous month’s <details> with open if you want it expanded by default.


    blog
    How to post articles

Duplicate a .bubble block and change:

href="#" → link to a full post page if/when you create it.

src="blog-YYYY-mm.jpg" → thumbnail image.

data-tags="regulation leadership" → space-separated topics.

Title, excerpt, and date.


contact
If you use Formspree, replace https://formspree.io/f/your-id with your form endpoint.

services
Replace svc-1.jpg, svc-2.jpg, svc-3.jpg with your images (same folder).

Change the service names inside each <figcaption>.

All cards currently link to contact.html. If you later create dedicated service pages, update the href accordingly.